  <title>GLib.OptionContext.prototype.add_group</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function add_group(group: <link xref="GLib.OptionGroup">GLib.OptionGroup</link>): void {
    // Gjs wrapper for g_option_context_add_group()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Adds a <link xref="GLib.OptionGroup"/> to the <code>context</code>, so that parsing with <code>context</code>
will recognize the options in the group. Note that the group will
be freed together with the context when <link xref="GLib.free"/> is
called, so you must not free the group yourself after adding it
to a context.</p>
  <p>Since 2.6</p>
